Be sure that this folder never is published as it may contain a private key.

SAML Python Toolkit expects that certs for the SP to be stored in this folder as:

 * sp.key     Private Key
 * sp.crt     Public Cert
 * sp_new.crt Future Public Cert


You can also use another cert to sign the metadata of the SP using:

 * metadata.key
 * metadata.crt
